```json
{
```

```json
{
  "name": "main-content",
  "match": {
    "selector": "div#app > div.main-content"
  }
}
```

The problem is that:
1. The DOM node paths are like `"HTML > BODY > DIV#app"` or similar
2. The container match selector is like `"div#app > div.main-content"`
3. These don't match exactly!
